            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each attack made targeting this unit, on a successful Saving Throw of 6, the unit which made that attack suffers SW equal to the D of that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Kastelan Protocols" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="b5ed-445b-1a2d-73e3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit Deploys or an ability has this unit ‘change protocol’, select one of the following abilities. Then, this unit gains the selected ability and loses any of the other abilities (if it has any):


Aegis Protocol: For each ranged attack that targets this unit, reroll a failed Saving Throw of 1 for that attack.


Conqueror Protocol: This unit’s M is improved to 9”.


Protector Protocol: For each attack this unit makes, add 1 to the Hit Roll for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
